headline: 2 Reasons to Avoid PAYX and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: While the broader market has struggled with the S&P 500 down 2.4% since November 2024, Paychex has surged ahead as its stock price has climbed by 7.5% to $156.18 per share. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
